  "description": "An economical washing machine with support for Samsung branded air bubble washing and an additional hatch for adding AddWash laundry. The model is presented on the market in 2021 and is positioned by the manufacturer in the middle price segment. At the heart of the Samsung AddWash WW70T552DTW washing machine is a reliable inverter motor and a drum with a capacity of up to 7 kg per cycle. At the same time, in one full cycle, the washing machine consumes on average only 34 liters of water, and the energy consumption corresponds to the economical class A +++ (103 kWh / year). A special small AddWash door allows you to reload forgotten clothes into the drum directly during washing. The software part is notable for a set of specialized washing modes, including a steam wash and Eco Bubble wash. The first provides clothes with an additional antibacterial effect, and the second will get rid of difficult stains even in cold water. The manufacturer also provides an intelligent system for personalizing settings and recommendations for washing programs. Among other things, the model can be controlled directly from the user's smartphone.",
